			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/52b1e66c479da917a064b5379f19eed2?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='u-photo avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.liraz.org' rel='external nofollow' class='u-url url'>Liraz Siri</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
