		<div class='e-content p-name p-summary'><p>I support text-only advertising on Wikipedia:<br />
1. being served directly by Wikipedia servers,<br />
2. from the same domain as other content,<br />
3. being managed by Wikipedia staff (like in newspaper ads, i.e. no uncontrolled 3rd party feeds).</p>
<p>I oppose any 3rd party-served ads, and graphics in all forms and shapes. Expect muzzle flashes if there&#8217;s ever a flash ad there (pun intended).</p>
