<p>I think users are savvy enough to recognize that the ad is trying to get them to buy something, my 5 year old niece knows that the ads on TV is trying to get her to do something that she doesn&#8217;t need to do. The articles (which is what we&#8217;re really talking about here) would still be as non-biased as always.</p>
