			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/?d=identicon&amp;s=32' class='u-photo avatar avatar-32 photo avatar-default' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn">Hinotori</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
